content: I'm so excited to start my hike to Charlies Bunion! Before I go, I just wanted to ask if you know of any good coffee shops in Gatlinburg where I can grab a cup of coffee before I head out? I've been driving a lot lately, including my recent road trip to Asheville, North Carolina, where I drove around 540 miles round-trip, and I could use a caffeine boost to start my day.
